title: Frames X 2
description:
Frames X is the ultimate web design system and Figma UI kit bundle, with multiple libraries, a growing collection of open-source code components, design tokens, interactive elements, dashboards, charts, and the largest collection of robust UI components in the world.

Frames X is an extensive toolkit that includes every possible UI component you might need to build a design system or enhance your brand. Developed since 2017, Frames X is the most feature-rich UI kit bundle available for Figma.
